  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a long journey, you sit down to play some games while flying to another planet. Unfortunately, your distraction caused an asteroid hit your rocket and wake up in an unfamiliar place. Explore dig,  fight, trade, level up, upgrade and build your way back to the space age for glory and and a new high score on your game. Trade with NPCs and Invest for a better future.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MINE RESOURCES AND CRAFT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dig your way through different layers to discover unique structures and collect resources. Craft your way to the space age by upgrading your tools with better resources, and craft machinery to help you automate the process of smelting and crafting.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE ENEMIES AND BOSSES IN UNDERGROUND COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills by fighting your way through big and small hostile dwellers in this underground frenzy. Level up your skills and build new weapons and armor to enhance your mining and combat abilities. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD, CRAFT AND AUTOMATE </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade and build your way back to the space age so you can make a rocket and get back to your \"important Business\" before you were rudely interrupted. Build glorious bases and create factories to accelerate your progress, avoid tedious work and imprint your mark upon the land.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE WITH ANOTHER PLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a friend to experience the unique world and fight underground monstrosities together in this 1-2 player mining and combat adventure.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a long journey, you sit down to play some games while flying to another planet. Unfortunately, your distraction caused an asteroid hit your rocket and wake up in an unfamiliar place. Explore dig,  fight, trade, level up, upgrade and build your way back to the space age for glory and and a new high score on your game. Trade with NPCs and Invest for a better future.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MINE RESOURCES AND CRAFT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/e9e9681820c46e0279c9bf64d91a4960.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dig your way through different layers to discover unique structures and collect resources. Craft your way to the space age by upgrading your tools with better resources, and craft machinery to help you automate the process of smelting and crafting.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLE ENEMIES AND BOSSES IN UNDERGROUND COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/f2b84d34430c58ad9ed7a8b7bb925295.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills by fighting your way through big and small hostile dwellers in this underground frenzy. Level up your skills and build new weapons and armor to enhance your mining and combat abilities. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD, CRAFT AND AUTOMATE </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/31e90cac61b4ada38c1fff578e243700.mp4?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade and build your way back to the space age so you can make a rocket and get back to your \"important Business\" before you were rudely interrupted. Build glorious bases and create factories to accelerate your progress, avoid tedious work and imprint your mark upon the land.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE WITH ANOTHER PLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.poster.avif?t=1767722518\" width=756 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.webm?t=1767722518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844650/extras/6e9535004519aa9fe58b0cbc9041dccb.mp4?t=17